reviews.text: Great place good music food is great but only downside is a little expensive!!

I live not too far from here. I love coming here when the weather is nice and we sit outside. On the weekends the place gets busy. The live singing is hit or miss. I love this veggie dumplings but and bread aptz. I would say the vegetarian options here are ok but not amazing. Service is good here.

reviews.text: 好抵食♡♡☺😘
原本覺得Ok，但進食時疴了3至4次，回到家仍然肚疴，以後不會再去。
音樂…正宗豬肘…甜品，假日好時光👍
環境普通，食品不過失，歡樂時段啤酒OK，樂隊表演好。服務Aㄧ。
好味道，吾錯，有停車場可泊車
